rows.label: qev050502_MSG0007
rows.name:
That guy is terrifying... The hell is he planning to do
here, anyway?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050502_MSG0001
rows.name:
Would you stop with the chitchat and report him to
the authorities already?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050502_MSG0002
rows.name: He seems like all bark and no bite, but still...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050502_MSG0003
rows.name: If he pulls a sword on us, it'll be a bloodbath![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050502_MSG0004
rows.name:
Oh, I dunno. He doesn't seem like a bad sort.
If I had a proper recipe or two, I wouldn't mind
walking him through them.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050502_MSG0005
rows.name: Try doing a lap of the city to see what folks suggest.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050502_MSG0006
rows.name:
There are plenty of gourmet types hereâ€”someone must
have a favorite recipe to recommend.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050502_MSG0010
rows.name:
And then a nice marbled suid fillet.
I should be able to put something together with that.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev050502_MSG0011
rows.name:
You're probably tired of doing errands for us by now,
but I appreciate it. Good luck.[ST:wait ]
